text: Free Entrance make sure to familiarise with the map before you visit if you planning to see the whole garden
Another part of Singapore Botanic Garden for one to explore.
Cameras here.. no parking by road side

Its botanic garden. Lots of trees and plants, fresh air and spacious. Great place for running or walking or picnic, theres lockers and vending machines near the toilet.

Theres also shops selling food nearby.
Excellent experience
Its a convenient way to enter the lower half of the Botanic Gardens and has a point where you can also park your bicycle!
